question.title: SpringBoot web application 404 not found error
question.body:
I am learning Spring Boot and while making a web app, I encountered WhiteLabel error page with status code 404. Below is my controller code

 @Controller
public class HomeController {
    @RequestMapping("/")
    public String home(){
        System.out.println("nskjdnwmndkjnwekd wklndwkelkx");
        return "index.jsp";
    }
}

This is my project structure. HomeController class is inside the Controller folder. I also added tomcat japser dependency in the pom file but still the error is same. i tried with adding jstl dependency also but didn't work.

Update: The project is working on Mac machines but not on windows. Any idea what could have gone wrong.
